    "description": "在<strong>《面具传说：维可历险记》</strong>中，你将扮演神秘的冒险家维可，在充满黑暗与秘密的世界中收集七副强大的始源面具。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/cec16b9844e325403af9a0229b472c5f.poster.avif?t=1732185375\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/cec16b9844e325403af9a0229b472c5f.webm?t=1732185375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/cec16b9844e325403af9a0229b472c5f.mp4?t=1732185375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>《面具传说：维可历险记》是一款巧妙融合了冒险和实时战斗的<strong>第三人称动作冒险游戏</strong>。作为勇敢的冒险家和面具收集者维可，你将<strong>探索一个逐渐开放、鼓励探索的世界</strong>，完成极具挑战的任务，战胜强大的敌人，利用面具的力量解决错综复杂的谜题，最终揭开这广阔世界的秘密。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/10414268d5c23343a475d1be8ed746e3.avif?t=1732185375\" width=608 height=139 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/c4863b758e771073a44ca5e032fec63b.poster.avif?t=1732185375\" width=704 height=396 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/c4863b758e771073a44ca5e032fec63b.webm?t=1732185375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/c4863b758e771073a44ca5e032fec63b.mp4?t=1732185375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>体验启发自《塞尔达传说：时之笛》及其作品的战斗系统，其中还加入了小部分类魂的机制，让游戏深度得到了提升。利用面具的独特能力，享受轻松有趣的战斗。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/7d15798c0bcc2d4407e215da04bfdde4.avif?t=1732185375\" width=609 height=139 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/d9f48094bfa78c3c368ec4a07a2d1e0e.poster.avif?t=1732185375\" width=798 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/d9f48094bfa78c3c368ec4a07a2d1e0e.webm?t=1732185375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/d9f48094bfa78c3c368ec4a07a2d1e0e.mp4?t=1732185375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>探索宽阔的世界，发现多样的风景。从如梦似幻的法师村到深沉低语的黑暗森林，每个场景都经过精心设计。地下深渊更是布满了危险的剧毒水域，等待最勇敢的冒险家前来挑战。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/b29c66e83805e8fe154bb366abd1d080.avif?t=1732185375\" width=609 height=139 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/d42fed170801a554e9af731fa3b9c356.poster.avif?t=1732185375\" width=662 height=372 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/d42fed170801a554e9af731fa3b9c356.webm?t=1732185375\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1682290/extras/d42fed170801a554e9af731fa3b9c356.mp4?t=1732185375\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>谜题无处不在！帮助老农找回失踪的动物，或是用智慧解开难机关，最终收集七副始源面具。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色：</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> 单人动作冒险游戏，启发自经典3D平台游戏和角色扮演游戏，例如《塞尔达传说：时之笛》、类魂游戏与《斯派罗》<br></li><li> 大量的可收集面具，能赋予维可独特的能力，帮助他完成冒险。您可以通过装备不同的面具完成构筑，无论是远距离作战还是近身搏斗都能手到擒来<br></li><li> 有趣的战斗机制，挑战您的技巧，同时也提供<strong>惬意的游戏体验</strong><br></li><li> 广阔而美丽的奇幻世界，充满着丰富多彩的角色、引人入胜的谜题和细致入微的探索环境<br></li><li> 以维可的旅程为主轴的感人故事，包含许多温馨时刻与挑战考验<br></li><li> 通关主线大约需要8-12小时，还有大量的支线与秘密等待您揭开<br></li><li> 完全支持手柄，可自定义按键，增强您的游戏体验</li></ul><br>",
